snippet.title: Gone Wandering | Release Trailer
snippet.description:
A girl, a boat and a whole lot of butterflies

Out now for FREE on PC and Mac here: oogaphobia.itch.io/gone-wandering


Gone Wandering is a relaxing collectathon game with puzzle elements, an interesting world to explore, and a Nintendo 64 aesthetic.

Twitter: @OogaphobiaClub - @Taboneous & @Austee_Frostee
Facebook: facebook.com/GoneWanderingGame
Itch.io: oogaphobia.itch.io/gone-wandering
Email: WeDontMakeGames@gmail.com
